videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Daniil Dubov vs Sergey Karjakin
Russian Championship Superfinal, ROUND 11
Giuoco Piano (C53)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Bc5 4. c3 Nf6 5. d4 exd4 6. b4 (The Delayed Evans!) Bb6 7. e5 Ne4 8. Bd5 Nxc3 9. Nxc3 dxc3 10. Bg5 Ne7 11. O-O h6 12. Bh4 O-O 13. Re1 Qe8 14. Bb3 a5 15. Bf6 a4 16. Bc4 Ng6 17. Qd3 d5 18. exd6 Be6 19.  Qxg6  Fxg6 20.  Rxe6  Qf7 21.  Bxc3  Kh8 22.  Re4  Qf5 23.  Re7  Rg8 24.  Bxg8  Rxg8 25.  Dxc7  Qc2 26.  Be5  Bxf2 + 27.  Kh1  Bb6 28.  H3  Kh7 29.  Re1  3a , 30.  Kh2  G5 31 .  Nd4  Qc4 32.  Nf5  Qxb4 33.  Rc1  Kg6 34.  Rxg7 +  Kxf5 35.  Rxg8 Bxc7 36.  Bxc7  Qb2 37.  Rc5 +  Ke4 38.  Rd8

The 73rd Russian Championship is a 12-player round-robin tournament taking place from 5-16 December 2020 in the Central Chess Club in Moscow, Russia.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: ruchess.ru
